269
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:34,850
I stayed by her side from day to night.

270
00:24:36,060 --> 00:24:38,530
But she never got better.

271
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,330
Later,

272
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:44,420
I went to my father.

273
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:48,250
But he wouldn't see her.

274
00:24:48,250 --> 00:24:50,140
 Mother. 

275
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:51,620
 Mother. 

276
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:54,110
 Please don't die. 

277
00:24:54,110 --> 00:24:56,880
 Please don't leave me. 

278
