 he loves you more than anyone in this world, 

287
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,630
 no matter what. 

288
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:37,430
 I won't ask you... 

289
00:25:39,210 --> 00:25:41,730
 to be a man of great achievements... 

290
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:48,100
 like your father. 

291
00:25:48,100 --> 00:25:50,560
 I only hope... 

292
00:25:52,820 --> 00:25:55,940
 that you can be happy. 

293
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:02,150
 This is my only wish. 

294
00:26:08,340 --> 00:26:10,910
 You are... 

295
00:26:13,570 --> 00:26:16,640
 on your own from now on. 

296
00:26:19,690 --> 00:26:22,180
 I can't keep you company anymore. 

297
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,920
 Mother! 

298
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:30,210
 Mother! 

299
00:26:30,210 --> 00:26:32,350
 Mother! 

300
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:35,350
 Please don't leave me! 

301
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:38,330
 Please! 

302
00:26:38,330 --> 00:26:42,170
 - Please!  
 - Until she passed away,

303
00:26:42,170 --> 00:26:45,960
my father hadn't seen her once.

304
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:48,130
I never understood...

305
00:26:49,610 --> 00:26:53,240
why my mother slowly lost my father's favor

306
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:59,220
and why my father abandoned my mother and me overnight.

307
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:06,070
I knew something was wrong the moment I saw this flower

308
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:08,640
on your mother's grave last night.

309
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:12,790
I have asked around about you at the Marquis's mansion.

310
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:15,350
All the servants told me the same story.

311
00:27:15,350 --> 00:27:20,350
They said that your mother cheated on your father.

312
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:22,550
She used her health condition

313
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:27,720
as an excuse to have an affair with a physician.

314
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:29,590
Nonsense!

315
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:31,070
My mother loved my father deeply.

316
00:27:31,070 --> 00:27:33,720
She wouldn't have done that.

317
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:35,900
Do you want the truth?

318
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:41,030
Jiang Xiang used to have an unremarkable maid.

319
00:27:41,030 --> 00:27:45,230
Five years ago, she was thrown out for doing something wrong.

320
00:27:45,230 --> 00:27:49,380
I managed to find her today and discovered the truth.

321
00:27:57,790 --> 00:27:59,620
Jiang Xiang instructed her

322
00:27:59,620 --> 00:28:04,810
to spread rumors about your mother having an affair with the physician.

323
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:09,170
 Don't make a scene. Let me handle it. 

324
00:28:09,170 --> 00:28:12,480
"If you want to accuse someone, it isn't hard to find excuses."

325
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:15,830
To destroy a woman, ruining her chastity

326
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:19,890
has been the most effective method for thousands of years.

327
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:24,340
If you still have doubts, I can bring you that maid.

328
00:28:24,340 --> 00:28:26,050
Talk to her.

329
00:28:27,070 --> 00:28:28,710
Does...

330
00:28:29,790 --> 00:28:31,870
my father know?

331
00:28:34,110 --> 00:28:35,830
I looked into it.

332
00:28:35,830 --> 00:28:39,340
His Majesty reclaimed military power from your father after he returned.

333
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:42,200
To gain a firm foothold in the court,

334
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,960
he desperately needed the help

335
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:46,760
of Jiang Xiang's father Jiang Jin, the Minister of Rites.

336
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:52,290
Presented with power, he chose Jiang Xiang.

337
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:57,710
I'm afraid that was when he started neglecting your mother.

338
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:06,060
And Jiang Xiang started poisoning my mother at that point.

339
00:29:20,270 --> 00:29:23,920
Of course, there are ways to find out

340
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:26,380
whether the Marquis was involved.

341
00:29:26,890 --> 00:29:28,612
But you will have to choose.

342
00:29:28,612 --> 00:29:31,020
Will you continue to investigate it...

343
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:36,530
or will you play dumb for the rest of your life?

344
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:53,880
My father has seen it.

345
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:55,790
He knows.

346
00:29:57,210 --> 00:30:00,560
He knows everything.

