00:30:33,750 --> 00:30:38,770
That's right. He conspired with Jiang Xiang to kill my mother.

355
00:30:40,100 --> 00:30:45,730
It seems he has long since stopped needing a son like me.

356
00:30:47,450 --> 00:30:50,210
I disagree, Second Young Master.

357
00:30:50,210 --> 00:30:53,340
The Marquis's love is not unchangeable.

358
00:30:53,340 --> 00:30:57,790
He used to love you because he loved your mother

359
00:30:57,790 --> 00:31:01,820
and because he thought you could carry on his mantle.

360
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:04,000
He now values your brother

361
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:07,210
because Jiang Xiang's maiden family was useful to him.

362
00:31:07,210 --> 00:31:11,590
Meanwhile, Jiang Xiang has made you a good-for-nothing.

363
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:16,830
He only likes those who are useful to him.

364
00:31:16,830 --> 00:31:21,170
Such affection is not difficult to come by.

365
00:31:21,170 --> 00:31:25,010
As long as you trust me and do as I say,

366
00:31:25,010 --> 00:31:29,030
I can help you get everything you want.

367
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:31,640
I just want to avenge my mother.

368
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:33,410
Jiang Xiang is easy to deal with.

369
00:31:33,410 --> 00:31:38,650
All she wants is to make Zhuang Zhifu the next Marquis.

370
00:31:38,650 --> 00:31:40,600
Once Zhuang Zhifu falls out of favor,

371
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:43,190
Jiang Xiang will have no one to rely on.

372
00:31:43,190 --> 00:31:48,690
The best revenge on her is to destroy her greatest hope.

373
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:52,200
She looks down on you at the moment.

374
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:54,790
It happens to be your greatest advantage.

375
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:57,490
Jiang Xiang deserves to die.

376
00:31:58,400 --> 00:32:04,170
But now, even my father has become my enemy.

377
00:32:10,130 --> 00:32:13,880
Zang Hai, y father is your enemy.

378
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:16,480
You want him dead to avenge your whole family.

379
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,820
But why are you helping me?

380
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:29,160
I need some information from the Marquis of Pingjin.

381
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:32,240
It's very important to me.

382
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:34,680
But you can't ask him.

383
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:37,070
You need someone to get that information for you.

384
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:39,030
That's right.

385
00:32:39,030 --> 00:32:41,000
My entire family was annihilated.

386
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:44,240
There are two other culprits besides your father.

387
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:47,140
One was the Seal-Holding Eunuch Director, Cao Jingjian.

388
00:32:47,140 --> 00:32:52,000
And I still haven't figured out who the other person is.

389
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:54,400
I have to find this person.

390
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:58,340
I can't afford to alert my enemy before then.

391
00:32:58,340 --> 00:33:02,690
You want me to figure out who this person is through my father.

392
00:33:02,690 --> 00:33:04,680
This is your condition for helping me?

393
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:06,240
That's right.

394
00:33:08,780 --> 00:33:12,860
Once you get an answer, what will you do?

395
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:26,650
I overstepped.

396
00:33:26,650 --> 00:33:29,690
You infiltrated into our house for revenge.

397
00:33:29,690 --> 00:33:32,240
I must take revenge.

398
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:38,020
If you won't let me, feel free to tell the Marquis who I am right now.

399
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:40,420
He killed my mother.

400
00:33:42,340 --> 00:33:44,770
I won't forgive him.

401
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:48,340
But still, he is my father.

402
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:54,750
The person who wiped out my family is right there

403
00:33:54,750 --> 00:33:57,640
but I can't kill him.

404
00:33:57,640 --> 00:34:00,720
Instead, I have to be close to him.

405
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:02,640
You know who killed your mother

406
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:06,840
yet you have to be his good son, showing respect and affection.

407
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:11,590
How is it not a harsh torment on you?

408
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:17,890
Blood for blood. This rule has remained unchanged for thousands of years.

409
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:29,040
I will try to help you.

410
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:32,270
But I'm not sure if I can help you take revenge.

411
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:38,190
Don't blame me if I change my mind.

412
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:41,510
You covered for me and helped me find my enemy.

413
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:45,340
I'm more than grateful. I won't ask for more.

414
00:34:45,340 --> 00:34:50,970
If you change your mind when the time comes, I won't complain.

415
00:34:55,710 --> 00:34:57,960
I shall honor our pact.

416
00:34:57,960 --> 00:35:00,070
Please help me take revenge.

417
00:35:00,070 --> 00:35:03,920
From now on, I will do whatever you say.

418
00:35:07,130 --> 00:35:12,770
From now on, we will share weal and woe.

419
00:35:30,590 --> 00:35:35,080
Within a year, I will help him become his father's most trusted son.

420
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:41,190
Once he figures out who the third culprit is, I'll carry out the plan.

421
00:35:43,050 --> 00:35:45,300
Even if you do your part,

422
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:48,440
what if he can't get anything out of his father in the end?

423
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,800
Can you wait?

424
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:52,840
I am enlightened.

425
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:57,500
I didn't bide my time for a decade just to win some petty battle.

426
00:35:57,500 --> 00:36:00,930
I will be more careful from now on.

427
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:07,490
Xiao Hai, let me tell you about Cao Jingxian.

428
00:36:08,740 --> 00:36:11,780
He appears to be merely colleagues with the Marquis of Pingjin.

429
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:16,270
But as the Vice Minister of Works, Zhuang Zhifu maintains the imperial gardens,

430
00:36:16,270 --> 00:36:19,630
and that involves the Directorate of Ceremonial.

431
00:36:19,630 --> 00:36:23,210
My guess is, that much of the money embezzled by Zhuang Zhifu

432
00:36:23,210 --> 00:36:26,510
has ended up in Cao Jingxian's pocket.

433
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,820
That's expected.

434
00:36:27,820 --> 00:36:31,150
Besides, he's surrounded by layers of security.

435
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:34,980
He's either in the palace or at his private residence in the capital.

436
00:36:34,980 --> 00:36:39,640
It's almost impossible to reach him.

437
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:45,960
But there'll be an opportunity in two months.

438
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:48,030
What are you referring to?

439
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:50,400
The ground polo competition held by the imperial court

440
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:53,000
to strengthen the fitness of men in Great Yong.

441
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:56,890
It's quite popular among the young masters of the noble families.

442
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:59,180
The Seal-Holding Eunuch Director

443
00:36:59,180 --> 00:37:02,850
brings rewards to the champion on behalf of His Majesty every year.

444
00:37:02,850 --> 00:37:06,770
That will be your chance to meet Cao Jingxian.

445
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:10,850
The opportunity comes at just the right time.

446
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:43,880
Aren't you tired of practicing Wuji Fist over and over again all day long?

447
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:47,190
- Try something else. 
 - You are the disciple and he is the master.

448
00:37:47,190 --> 00:37:49,490
And you're slacking off here?

449
00:37:49,490 --> 00:37:51,610
Zhinu, what brings you here?

450
00:37:51,610 --> 00:37:55,770
What did I tell you? Call me Zang Hai from now on.

451
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:02,190
Isn't this Second Young Master Zhuang?

452
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:04,510
You recognize me?

453
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:08,870
Sir, why did you ask me out and bring me here?

454
00:38:08,870 --> 00:38:12,040
You are going to practice martial arts here.

455
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:15,180
Since you want to regain your father's favor,

456
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:17,880
then you can't follow your brother's path.

457
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,840
We have to find another way.

458
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:22,690
We must convince your father that you have the potential

459
00:38:22,690 --> 00:38:24,680
to inherit his mantle.

460
00:38:24,680 --> 00:38:27,960
Shi Lei, see if he is cut out to be a martial artist.

461
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:29,660
All right.

462
00:38:33,150 --> 00:38:36,640
Are you crazy? His father is the Marquis of Pingjin.

463
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:39,060
What if he figures out who you are?

464
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:40,590
He already knows.

465
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:43,960
- Then... 
 - Of course, he also knows who you are.

466
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:46,800
Then why is he still alive?

467
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:50,440
Rest assured. He has allied with me.

468
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:53,710
He will be practicing martial arts here.

469
00:38:53,710 --> 00:38:56,790
Make sure Shi Lei teaches him well.

470
00:38:57,590 --> 00:39:00,150
Disciple, he is more gifted than you.

471
00:39:00,150 --> 00:39:01,840
I see potential in him.

472
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:03,630
Shut up.

473
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:08,190
He idles around and does nothing all day long.

474
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:09,840
Will he be able to do it?

475
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:12,480
That depends on your ability.

476
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:14,760
I'm entrusting him to you two.

477
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:18,510
You have two months to make him a martial artist.

478
00:39:18,510 --> 00:39:21,540
Sir, can we go somewhere else?

479
00:39:21,540 --> 00:39:24,780
This place is run down. I don't even see a decent table.

480
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:29,250
Besides, where do I sleep? So...

481
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:34,780
I'll stop.

482
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:37,960
Sir, it's fine here.

483
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:42,460
From now on, learn martial arts from these two masters.

484
00:39:43,190 --> 00:39:47,680
Remember. You promised to do whatever I say.

485
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:51,530
This is your first step toward a transformation.

486
00:39:51,530 --> 00:39:53,320
Of course, I'll be busy, too.

487
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:57,180
I have to work on your reputation in the capital.

488
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:05,160
Fists facing down.

489
00:40:07,410 --> 00:40:10,000
Can you squat properly or not?

490
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,230
Yes, I can.

491
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:13,030
Look at me.

492
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:16,920
This is a proper horse stance.

493
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,730
I see.

494
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:24,360
Can I have a bite?

495
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,880
Don't slack off.

496
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,710
I'm thirsty and hungry.

497
00:40:27,710 --> 00:40:29,610
Let me have a bite, please.

498
00:40:29,610 --> 00:40:31,320
Keep practicing and we'll see.

499
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:33,570
Turn around. Squat.

