00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:44,660
Official Lu, please let me see Eunuch Cao for a second.

502
00:40:44,660 --> 00:40:47,780
I will be reassured as long as everything is all right.

503
00:40:47,780 --> 00:40:51,420
Why do you want to see our ord, Official Chu?

504
00:40:56,510 --> 00:40:58,400
I observed the celestial signs.

505
00:40:58,400 --> 00:41:00,400
The Mandate Star shone brightly.

506
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:02,000
I read the signs.

507
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:04,230
Eunuch Cao serves as His Majesty's closest court official.

508
00:41:04,230 --> 00:41:06,670
So, he is the Mandate Star.

509
00:41:06,670 --> 00:41:08,230
Great news is to be expected.

510
00:41:08,230 --> 00:41:10,960
- I... 
 - Since you don't have something to say,

511
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:13,120
please go back, Official Chu.

512
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:21,230
I was humiliated by others.

513
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,880
Please do me justice.

514
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,440
Official Chu,

515
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:28,360
you are the Imperial Astronomer, a fifth-rank official.

516
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,760
Who dares to humiliate you?

517
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:32,960
I feel embarrassed.

518
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:35,880
I am being humiliated by the aide, Zang Hai, of the Marquis of Pingjin.

519
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:38,230
This person is insidious and vicious.

520
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:40,280
And he has become the top aide to the Marquis.

521
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,320
I have offended him.

522
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:43,800
I'm afraid that he is going to target me.

523
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:46,230
I seek your protection.

524
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:49,590
